## Notes

- `camera__initialize_camera__sets_fulcrum` also calls `initialize_camera`
  with `z_near = 0, z_far = 0` but does NOT call `is_camera__active`, so
  it passes without issue.
- The abort (signal 6) is a downstream effect of the munit assertion failure,
  not a crash in the camera code itself.
